      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>wholewheat penne </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain the<strong> wholewheat penne</strong></p><p>Re-boil a kettle</p>",
